{
  "title": "ISic001679. I.Sicily inscription 001679",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Διὶ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διὶ\">Δι̣ὶ̣</span></span> ὁ δᾶμ[ος τῶν Ἐγεσταίων] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡράκλειον Νύμφωνος Πε\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡράκλειον\">Ἡράκλειον</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\">Νύμφωνος</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πε\"><span data-text=\"Πε\">Πε̣</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἀρετᾶς ἕνεκα </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Διὶ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Διὶ\">Δ..</span></span>ΟΔΑΜ[..............]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡράκλειον Νύμφωνος Πε\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡράκλειον\">ΗΡΑΚΛΕΙΟΝ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Νύμφωνος\">ΝΥΜΦΩΝΟΣ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πε\"><span data-text=\"Πε\">Π.</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΑΡΕΤΑΣΕΝΕΚΑ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of I.Segesta</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>To Zeus. The people of the Segestans (have dedicated this statue of) Herakleios Pe[---] son of Nymphon, on account of his excellence</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a class=\"translation-source\" href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR</a></p>  <p>A Zeus. Il popolo dei Segestani (ha onorator/ha eretto la statua di) Herakleios, figlio di Nymphon, Pe[---], per il suo valore [transl. from I.Segesta]</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036</a></li></ul>  <ul><li> De Cesare, Parra 2001 418 with n.6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002470\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002470</a></li><li> Ampolo et al 2010 523 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002469\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002469</a></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-3  25-35  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence </div>",
